      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds incredibly positive. I'm glad to hear that. \n\nJust so I'm clear for the Q&A portion of the board meeting: did we meet the primary endpoint for the overall study population? I want to make sure I can answer any technical questions about the statistical significance of the main results if they dig into the numbers.",
